## Purge profile

```shell
# Purge using phone number
curl --location --request DELETE 'https://<%= config[:api_endpoint] %>/profile/purge' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--header 'Cookie: did=7Hvlb6ftsK; r46_debug=true' \
--data '{
    "shop_id": "...",
    "shop_secret": "...",
    "phone": "..."
}'

# Purge using email
curl --location --request DELETE 'https://<%= config[:api_endpoint] %>/profile/purge' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--header 'Cookie: did=7Hvlb6ftsK; r46_debug=true' \
--data '{
    "shop_id": "...",
    "shop_secret": "...",
    "email": "..."
}'
```

